{"tid":2256560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣51人接種流感疫苗現不良反應 12宗屬嚴重","createTime":"2020-10-24T12:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T12:41:09.000Z","uid":278767,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dfbf410aa50802e5354ada641a23a8b793c01c21","tid":2256560,"uid":278767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/v2/article/QB76QG?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fv2%2Farticle%2FQB76QG%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=108da38a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/v2/article/QB76QG?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n更新於 5分鐘前 &bull; 發布於 3小時前<br />\n台灣有51人接種流感疫苗後出現不良反應，其中12宗屬於嚴重不良反應。疾病管制署表示，嚴重不良反應不一定和疫苗有關，可能只是兩者發生時間剛好相近，台灣流感疫苗至今未有出現異常警訊。<br />\n南韓接連出現接種流感疫苗後死亡的個案，當中包括台灣也有使用的法國賽諾菲疫苗。當局表示，全台已接種400多萬劑流感疫苗，其中12人有嚴重不良反應，包括出現心肌炎、休克、呼吸困難等，另外39人有非嚴重的不良反應，例如頭暈、頭痛、紅疹、紅腫、發燒等。另外，51宗不良反應個案中，賽諾菲疫苗佔12宗，其中1宗為嚴重不良反應，接種者出現心肌炎。"},{"pid":"19d4a3709cba36fad3e209a4698fa3cce4cb38ca","tid":2256560,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T12:27:04.000Z","msg":"好驚好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0947859e953b92e6f51c1fad844205bef07bbcd","tid":2256560,"uid":214679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T12:36:10.000Z","msg":"51 / 4,000,000  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e8565a186726148c89382a6a8fc2066c865603","tid":2256560,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T12:41:09.000Z","msg":"最近咁多單係咪有批貨出事？"}]}